# SPEC-01-08 Anchor

## Definition

An Anchor connects knowledge to implementation evidence.

## Specification

An Anchor SHALL identify a location inside a source artifact.

An Anchor MUST have a stable identifier.

An Anchor MUST NOT depend on line numbers.

The compiler SHALL resolve Anchors to physical locations.

Anchors MAY exist in any supported text artifact.

## Example

```
// graphite:anchor checkout.validation

validateCheckout()
```
